msgid "Employees"
msgstr "Werknemers"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:7
msgid ""
"Odoo **Employees** centralizes :doc:`personnel files <employees/"
"new_employee>`, employment :doc:`contracts <payroll/contracts>`, "
"and :doc:`departmental hierarchies <employees/departments>` in one system. "
"In addition, each employee record tracks :doc:`certifications <employees/"
"certifications>` and :doc:`training <employees/learning>`, "
"earned :doc:`badges <employees/badges>`, and all assigned :doc:`equipment "
"<employees/equipment>`. Customizable :doc:`onboarding <employees/"
"onboarding>` and :doc:`offboarding <employees/offboarding>` programs ensure "
"all employees are trained and ready for work, and all required steps are "
"taken when they leave."
msgstr ""
"Odoo **Werknemers** centraliseert :doc:`personeelsdossiers <employees/"
"new_employee>`, arbeids:doc:`contracten <payroll/contracts>`, en "
":doc:`afdelingshiërarchieën <employees/departments>` in één systeem. "
"Daarnaast registreert elk werknemersdossier :doc:`certificeringen <employees/"
"certifications>` en :doc:`trainingen <employees/learning>`, verdiende "
":doc:`badges <employees/badges>`, en alle toegewezen :doc:`apparatuur "
"<employees/equipment>`. Aanpasbare :doc:`onboardingprogramma's <employees/"
"onboarding>` en :doc:`offboardingprogramma's <employees/offboarding>` zorgen "
"ervoor dat alle werknemers zijn getraind en klaar zijn voor het werk, en dat "
"alle vereiste stappen worden genomen wanneer ze vertrekken."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/employees.rst:16
msgid ""
"Properly configuring the settings in the **Employees** app ensures the "
"dashboard shows each employee's real-time attendance and work location—data "
"that drives payroll accuracy, capacity planning, and compliance reporting."
msgstr ""
"Het correct configureren van de instellingen in de app **Werknemers** zorgt "
"ervoor dat het dashboard de realtime aanwezigheid en werklocatie van elke "
"werknemer weergeeft—gegevens die de nauwkeurigheid van de loonadministratie, "
"capaciteitsplanning en nalevingsrapportage ondersteunen."

