msgid ""
"When receiving the bank statement in Odoo, you can now match the statement "
"line with the batch payment in one click. The payment is not reconciled "
"against the payslip batch, and all individual payslips."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer je het bankafschrift in Odoo ontvangt, kun je nu de afschriftregel "
"in één klik koppelen aan de batchbetaling. De betaling wordt afgeletterd "
"tegen de loonstrookbatch en alle afzonderlijke loonstroken."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:None
