msgstr ":guilabel:`Previous Payroll ID` (één per werknemer)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:472
msgid ""
"Ask your previous software provider if you cannot find its BMS ID or your "
"employees' payroll IDs."
msgstr ""
"Vraag je vorige softwareprovider als je het BMS-ID of de loonadministratie-"
"ID's van je werknemers niet kunt vinden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/australia.rst:None
