"Links payroll and accounting by creating journal entries to record payroll "
"in the company's books."
msgstr ""
"Koppelt loonadministratie en boekhouding door dagboekboekingen aan te maken "
"om de loonadministratie in de boeken van het bedrijf vast te leggen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:39
msgid ""
"Before configuring the Jordan localization, refer to the "
"general :doc:`payroll <../../payroll>` documentation, which includes the "
"basic information for all localizations, as well as all universal settings "
"and fields."
msgstr ""
"Raadpleeg de algemene :doc:`loonadministratie <../../payroll>`-documentatie "
"voordat je de Jordanië-lokalisatie configureert. Deze bevat de "
"basisinformatie voor alle lokalisaties, evenals alle universele instellingen "
"en velden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:44
msgid ""
":doc:`Jordan fiscal localization documentation <../../../finance/"
"fiscal_localizations/jordan>`"
msgstr ""
":doc:`Documentatie Jordaanse fiscale lokalisatie <../../../finance/"
"fiscal_localizations/jordan>`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:54
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Address`: Complete the full address, including "
"the :guilabel:`City`, :guilabel:`Zip Code`, and :guilabel:`Country` fields."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Adres`: Vul het volledige adres in, inclusief de velden "
":guilabel:`Plaats`, :guilabel:`Postcode` en :guilabel:`Land`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:58
msgid ""
"Jordan does not use the :guilabel:`State` field, this remains blank. "
"The :guilabel:`Zip Code` refers to the Jordanian `Postal Code`."
msgstr ""
"Jordanië gebruikt het veld :guilabel:`Staat` niet, dit blijft leeg. De "
":guilabel:`Postcode` verwijst naar de Jordaanse `Postal Code`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:61
msgid ":guilabel:`Tax ID`: Enter the company's tax identification number."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Btw-nummer`: Voer het fiscaal identificatienummer van het bedrijf "
"in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:62
msgid ":guilabel:`Company ID` : Enter the business's registry number."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Bedrijfs-ID`: Voer het registratienummer van het bedrijf in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:63
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Currency`: By default, :abbr:`JOD (Jordanian Dollars)` is "
"selected. If not, select :guilabel:`JOD` from the drop-down menu."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Valuta`: Standaard is :abbr:`JOD (Jordaanse dollars)` "
"geselecteerd. Zo niet, selecteer dan :guilabel:`JOD` uit het "
"vervolgkeuzemenu."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:69
msgid ""
"Every employee being paid must have their employee profiles configured for "
"the Jordan payroll localization. Additional fields are present after "
"configuring the database for Jordan."
msgstr ""
"Elke werknemer die wordt betaald, moet zijn werknemersprofiel geconfigureerd "
"hebben voor de Jordanië-lokalisatie van de loonadministratie. Extra velden "
"zijn aanwezig na het configureren van de database voor Jordanië."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:72
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:91
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:74
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:63
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:102
msgid ""
"To update an employee form, open the :menuselection:`Employees` app and "
"click on the desired employee record. On the employee form, configure the "
"required fields in the related tabs."
msgstr ""
"Om een werknemersformulier bij te werken, open je de app "
":menuselection:`Werknemers` en klik je op het gewenste werknemersrecord. "
"Configureer op het werknemersformulier de vereiste velden in de gerelateerde "
"tabbladen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:78
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:97
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:80
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:69
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:108
msgid ""
"Enter the :guilabel:`Work Address` for the employee in "
"the :guilabel:`Location` section of the :guilabel:`Work` tab."
msgstr ""
"Voer het :guilabel:`Werkadres` voor de werknemer in het gedeelte "
":guilabel:`Locatie` van het tabblad :guilabel:`Werk` in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:84
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:107
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:89
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:75
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:118
msgid ""
"Ensure the employee has a minimum of one :ref:`trusted bank account "
"<employees/private-contact>` listed in the :guilabel:`Bank Accounts` field "
"in the :guilabel:`Private Contact` section."
msgstr ""
"Zorg ervoor dat de werknemer minimaal één :ref:`vertrouwde bankrekening "
"<employees/private-contact>` heeft vermeld in het veld "
":guilabel:`Bankrekeningen` in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Privécontact`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:87
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:110
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:78
msgid ""
"These accounts are used to pay the employee. Payroll **cannot** be processed "
"for employees without a *trusted* :ref:`bank account <employees/private-"
"contact>`. If no trusted bank account is set, a warning appears on the "
"**Payroll** dashboard and an error occurs when attempting to run payroll."
msgstr ""
"Deze rekeningen worden gebruikt om de werknemer te betalen. "
"Loonadministratie **kan niet** worden verwerkt voor werknemers zonder een "
"*vertrouwde* :ref:`bankrekening <employees/private-contact>`. Als er geen "
"vertrouwde bankrekening is ingesteld, verschijnt er een waarschuwing op het "
"**Loonadministratie**-dashboard en treedt er een fout op bij het uitvoeren "
"van de loonadministratie."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:91
msgid ""
"If the employee is **not** a resident of Jordan, tick the :guilabel:`Non-"
"resident` box. This indicates the employee is *not* eligible for personal "
"exemptions."
msgstr ""
"Als de werknemer **geen** inwoner van Jordanië is, vink je het vakje "
":guilabel:`Niet-ingezetene` aan. Dit geeft aan dat de werknemer *niet* in "
"aanmerking komt voor persoonlijke vrijstellingen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:94
msgid ""
"Under the :guilabel:`Family` section, ensure the :guilabel:`Has Dependants` "
"box is ticked if the employee has any dependants, such as a spouse, "
"children, or parents. This ensures they receive an additional exemption on "
"their taxable salary."
msgstr ""
"Zorg er in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Familie` voor dat het selectievakje "
":guilabel:`Heeft afhankelijke personen` is aangevinkt als de werknemer "
"afhankelijke personen heeft, zoals een echtgenoot, kinderen of ouders. Dit "
"zorgt ervoor dat ze een extra vrijstelling krijgen op hun belastbaar salaris."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:98
msgid ""
"By default, the :guilabel:`Is Eligible for EOS` checkbox is ticked, in "
"the :guilabel:`Personal Information` section, indicating the employee is "
"eligible for end of service benefits. If the employee is **not** eligible, "
"ensure the box is unchecked."
msgstr ""
"Standaard is het selectievakje :guilabel:`Komt in aanmerking voor EOS` "
"aangevinkt in het gedeelte :guilabel:`Persoonlijke informatie`, wat aangeeft "
"dat de werknemer in aanmerking komt voor uitkeringen bij einde "
"dienstverband. Als de werknemer **niet** in aanmerking komt, zorg er dan "
"voor dat het vakje is uitgevinkt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:102
msgid ""
"Additionally, if the employee is blind, tick the :guilabel:`Is Blind` "
"checkbox. This ensures the employee's entire salary is tax-exempt."
msgstr ""
"Als de werknemer blind is, vink je bovendien het selectievakje :guilabel:`Is "
"blind` aan. Dit zorgt ervoor dat het volledige salaris van de werknemer is "
"vrijgesteld van belasting."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:111
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:136
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:108
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:90
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:138
msgid ""
"This section holds information that drives salary calculations. Ensure the "
"following fields are configured:"
msgstr ""
"Deze sectie bevat informatie die salarisberekeningen aanstuurt. Zorg ervoor "
"dat de volgende velden zijn geconfigureerd:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:114
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract`: Ensure the contract dates are populated. The contract "
"start date populates the first field, and if the contract has a set end "
"date, that is populated in the second field."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Contract`: Zorg ervoor dat de contractdata zijn ingevuld. De "
"startdatum van het contract vult het eerste veld, en als het contract een "
"vaste einddatum heeft, wordt die in het tweede veld ingevuld."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:116
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:141
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:113
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:94
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:143
msgid ":guilabel:`Wage Type`: Select how the employee is paid."
msgstr ":guilabel:`Loontype`: Selecteer hoe de werknemer wordt betaald."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:118
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:143
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:115
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:96
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:145
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Fixed Wage` for salaried employees who receive the same "
"amount each pay period."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer :guilabel:`Vast loon` voor werknemers met een vast salaris die "
"elke betaalperiode hetzelfde bedrag ontvangen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:120
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:145
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:117
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:98
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:147
msgid ""
"Select :guilabel:`Hourly Wage` for employees paid based on hours worked."
msgstr ""
"Selecteer :guilabel:`Uurloon` voor werknemers die worden betaald op basis "
"van gewerkte uren."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:123
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:120
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:101
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:150
msgid ""
"Set a default :guilabel:`Wage Type` in the salary :ref:`Structure Type "
"<payroll/structure-types>` to configure employees in bulk. If needed, the "
"default can be overridden on individual employee records if exceptions are "
"needed."
msgstr ""
"Stel een standaard :guilabel:`Loontype` in het salaris :ref:`Structuurtype "
"<payroll/structure-types>` in om werknemers bulksgewijs te configureren. "
"Indien nodig kan de standaard worden overschreven op individuele "
"werknemersrecords als er uitzonderingen nodig zijn."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:127
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Wage`: Enter the monthly wage in this field, in :abbr:`JOD "
"(Jordanian Dollars)`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Loon`: Voer het maandloon in dit veld in, in :abbr:`JOD "
"(Jordaanse dollar)`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:128
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Employee Type`: Select what kind of employee the contract is for, "
"such as :guilabel:`Employee` or :guilabel:`Freelance`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Werknemerstype`: Selecteer voor wat voor soort werknemer het "
"contract is, zoals :guilabel:`Werknemer` of :guilabel:`Freelancer`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:130
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:124
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Contract Type`: Determines how the employee is paid and "
"classified, such "
"as :guilabel:`Permanent`, :guilabel:`Temporary`, :guilabel:`Seasonal`."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Contracttype`: Bepaalt hoe de werknemer wordt betaald en "
"geclassificeerd, zoals :guilabel:`Vast`, :guilabel:`Tijdelijk`, "
":guilabel:`Seizoensgebonden`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:132
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Pay Category`: Select :guilabel:`Jordan: Employee` for this "
"field. This defines when the employee is paid, their default working "
"schedule, and the work entry type it applies to."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Salariscategorie`: Selecteer :guilabel:`Jordanië: Werknemer` voor "
"dit veld. Dit bepaalt wanneer de werknemer wordt betaald, hun standaard "
"werkrooster en het werkboekingstype waarop het van toepassing is."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "The contract overview section of the employee form of the payroll tab."
msgstr ""
"Het sectie contractoverzicht van het werknemersformulier van het tabblad "
"loonadministratie."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:141
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:136
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:123
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:170
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Work Entry Source`: Defines how :doc:`work entries <../"
"work_entries>` are generated for payroll during the specified pay period. "
"The options are:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Bron werkboeking`: Bepaalt hoe :doc:`werkboekingen <../"
"work_entries>` worden gegenereerd voor loonadministratie tijdens de "
"opgegeven loonadministratieperiode. De opties zijn:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:144
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:139
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:126
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:173
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Schedule`: Based on the employee's assigned :ref:`working "
"schedule <employees/schedule>` (e.g., 40 hours per week)."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Werkrooster`: Gebaseerd op het toegewezen :ref:`werkrooster "
"<employees/schedule>` van de werknemer (bv. 40 uur per week)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:141
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:128
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:175
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Attendances`: Based on :doc:`approved checked-in hours <../../"
"attendances/management>` in the **Attendances** app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Aanwezigheid`: Gebaseerd op :doc:`goedgekeurde ingeklokte uren "
"<../../attendances/management>` in de **Aanwezigheid** app."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:148
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:143
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:130
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:177
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Planning`: Based on :ref:`scheduled shifts <planning/shifts>` in "
"the **Planning** app."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Planning`: Gebaseerd op :ref:`geplande shifts <planning/shifts>` "
"in de **Planning** app."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:151
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:146
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:180
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Extra Hours`: Tick the checkbox to allow the **Attendances** app "
"to add any extra work entries logged by the employee."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Extra uren`: Vink het selectievakje aan om de **Aanwezigheid** "
"app toe te staan extra werkboekingen toe te voegen die door de werknemer "
"zijn geregistreerd."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:153
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Working Hours`: Using the drop-down menu, "
"select :guilabel:`Jordan Working Schedule`, which consists of a Sunday - "
"Thursday, 40-hour work week."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Werkuren`: Selecteer via het vervolgkeuzemenu :guilabel:`Jordanië "
"werkrooster`, dat bestaat uit een zondag - donderdag werkweek van 40 uur."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:157
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:165
msgid "Allowances section"
msgstr "Gedeelte toelagen"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:159
msgid ""
"The following sections of benefits are considered common ones offered by "
"Jordanian employers. This information needs to be populated with the "
"information selected by the employee."
msgstr ""
"De volgende gedeelten met voorzieningen worden beschouwd als veel "
"voorkomende voorzieningen die door Jordaanse werkgevers worden aangeboden. "
"Deze informatie moet worden ingevuld met de informatie die door de werknemer "
"is geselecteerd."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:163
msgid ""
"The benefits listed in this section are considered the ones most commonly "
"offered by companies. If other employee benefits exist that require regular "
"paycheck deductions, they can be added as *inputs*."
msgstr ""
"De voorzieningen die in dit gedeelte worden vermeld, worden beschouwd als de "
"meest voorkomende die door bedrijven worden aangeboden. Als er andere "
"personeelsvoorzieningen bestaan waarvoor regelmatige inhoudingen op het "
"salaris nodig zijn, kunnen ze worden toegevoegd als *invoer*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:167
msgid ""
"Enter the monthly allowance amount "
"for :guilabel:`Housing`, :guilabel:`Transportation`, and :guilabel:`Other` "
"allowances."
msgstr ""
"Voer het maandelijkse toelage bedrag in voor :guilabel:`Huisvesting`, "
":guilabel:`Vervoer` en :guilabel:`Overige` toelagen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:170
msgid ""
"If the employee is tax exempt, enter the annual amount that is not subject "
"to taxes in the :guilabel:`Tax Exemption` field."
msgstr ""
"Als de werknemer is vrijgesteld van belasting, voer dan het jaarlijkse "
"bedrag dat niet onderworpen is aan belasting in het veld "
":guilabel:`Belastingvrijstelling` in."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:173
msgid ""
"If the employee's salary is based on commission, tick the :guilabel:`Is "
"Commission based` checkbox."
msgstr ""
"Als het salaris van de werknemer gebaseerd is op commissie, vink je het "
"selectievakje :guilabel:`Is gebaseerd op commissie` aan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:176
msgid "Annual leave provision section"
msgstr "Gedeelte jaarlijkse verlofvoorziening"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:178
msgid ""
"Every year, employees receive days off. Enter the number of days in "
"the :guilabel:`Number of Leave days` field. The default value is 14."
msgstr ""
"Elk jaar krijgen werknemers vrije dagen. Voer het aantal dagen in het veld "
":guilabel:`Aantal verlofdagen` in. De standaardwaarde is 14."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:182
msgid "Social Insurance"
msgstr "Sociale verzekering"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:184
msgid ""
"Social insurance rules calculate the contribution amounts that are to be "
"paid by the employer and employee to the :abbr:`Social Security Corporation "
"(SSC)`. This is only available for Jordanian employees."
msgstr ""
"Regels voor sociale verzekering berekenen de bijdragebedragen die door de "
"werkgever en werknemer moeten worden betaald aan de "
":abbr:`Socialezekerheidsinstelling (SSC)`. Dit is alleen beschikbaar voor "
"Jordaanse werknemers."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:188
msgid ""
"The employer contributes 14.25% of the employee's salary to "
"the :abbr:`Social Security Corporation (SSC)`, while the employee "
"contributes 7.5% of their salary, which is deducted from their payslip."
msgstr ""
"De werkgever draagt 14,25% van het salaris van de werknemer af aan de "
":abbr:`Socialezekerheidsinstelling (SSC)`, terwijl de werknemer 7,5% van hun "
"salaris bijdraagt, wat wordt ingehouden op hun loonstrook."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:191
msgid ""
"For both employer and employee contributions, the base amount on which they "
"are calculated is bound by a cap that gets updated every year."
msgstr ""
"Voor zowel werkgevers- als werknemersbijdragen wordt het basisbedrag waarop "
"ze worden berekend begrensd door een maximum dat elk jaar wordt bijgewerkt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:197
msgid "The following leave types are available to employees working in Jordan:"
msgstr "De volgende verloftypes zijn beschikbaar voor werknemers in Jordanië:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:199
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Annual leave`: Employee's are eligible for 21 days of annual "
"leave, and if the employee requires more days, they have to be requested "
"from HR managers accordingly."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Jaarlijks verlof`: Werknemers hebben recht op 21 dagen jaarlijks "
"verlof. Als de werknemer meer dagen nodig heeft, moeten deze "
"dienovereenkomstig bij de HR-managers worden aangevraagd."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:206
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Sick leave`: Employee's working in Jordan are entitled to 14 days "
"of paid sick leave per year, with the possibility of an additional 14 days "
"if hospitalized. No deductions are applied to the employee in those cases."
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Ziekteverlof`: Werknemers in Jordanië hebben recht op 14 dagen "
"betaald ziekteverlof per jaar, met de mogelijkheid van nog eens 14 dagen bij "
"ziekenhuisopname. In die gevallen worden er geen inhoudingen toegepast op de "
"werknemer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:210
msgid ""
":guilabel:`Other leave types`: These leave types are fully paid and do not "
"affect the final payslip, but are tracked for reporting purposes:"
msgstr ""
":guilabel:`Andere verloftypes`: Deze verloftypes worden volledig betaald en "
"hebben geen invloed op de uiteindelijke loonstrook, maar worden bijgehouden "
"voor rapportagedoeleinden:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:213
msgid ":guilabel:`Maternity leave`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Zwangerschapsverlof`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:214
msgid ":guilabel:`Paternity Leave`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Vaderschapsverlof`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:215
msgid ":guilabel:`Pilgrimage Leave`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Bedevaartsverlof`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:216
msgid ":guilabel:`Study leave`"
msgstr ":guilabel:`Studieverlof`"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:219
msgid "Income Tax"
msgstr "Inkomstenbelasting"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:221
msgid ""
"In Jordan, employees are subject to a progressive income tax system, where "
"tax rates increase with higher annual income brackets."
msgstr ""
"In Jordanië zijn werknemers onderworpen aan een progressief "
"inkomstenbelastingsysteem, waarbij de belastingtarieven stijgen bij hogere "
"jaarlijkse inkomensschijven."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:233
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:262
msgid "Taxable Bracket"
msgstr "Belastbare schijf"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:234
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:263
msgid "Range"
msgstr "Bereik"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:235
msgid "5%"
msgstr "5%"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:236
msgid "0-5,000"
msgstr "0-5.000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:238
msgid "5,001 - 10,000"
msgstr "5.001 - 10.000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:240
msgid "10,001 - 15,000"
msgstr "10.001 - 15.000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:242
msgid "15,001 - 20,000"
msgstr "15.001 - 20.000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:244
msgid "20,001 - 1,000,000"
msgstr "20.001 - 1.000.000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:245
msgid "30%"
msgstr "30%"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:246
msgid "More than 1,000,000"
msgstr "Meer dan 1.000.000"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:249
msgid ""
"Tax brackets are applied progressively. This means each portion of an "
"employee's income is taxed at its respective rate within each bracket, "
"rather than their entire income being taxed at the rate of the highest "
"bracket they fall into."
msgstr ""
"Belastingschijven worden progressief toegepast. Dit betekent dat elk deel "
"van het inkomen van een werknemer wordt belast tegen het respectieve tarief "
"binnen elke schijf, in plaats van dat het volledige inkomen wordt belast "
"tegen het tarief van de hoogste schijf waarin ze vallen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:256
msgid ""
"Several factors contribute to exempting part of an employee's gross income, "
"including:"
msgstr ""
"Verschillende factoren dragen bij aan de vrijstelling van een deel van het "
"bruto-inkomen van een werknemer, waaronder:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:258
msgid ""
"**Jordanian residency**: Residents are entitled to a yearly exemption of "
"12,000 JOD."
msgstr ""
"**Jordaanse verblijfsstatus**: Inwoners hebben recht op een jaarlijkse "
"vrijstelling van 12.000 JOD."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:259
msgid ""
"**Blindness**: Individuals who are blind are **fully** exempt from income "
"tax."
msgstr ""
"**Blindheid**: Personen die blind zijn, zijn **volledig** vrijgesteld van "
"inkomstenbelasting."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:260
msgid ""
"**Dependents**: An additional 12,000 JOD exemption per year for employees "
"with dependents."
msgstr ""
"**Afhankelijke personen**: Een extra vrijstelling van 12.000 JOD per jaar "
"voor werknemers met afhankelijke personen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:265
msgid ""
"Employees are entitled to additional pay for overtime worked, depending on "
"when the overtime hours are worked:"
msgstr ""
"Werknemers hebben recht op extra betaling voor gewerkte overuren, "
"afhankelijk van wanneer de overuren worden gewerkt:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:268
msgid ""
"On working days: Overtime is paid at 1.25 times the regular hourly wage."
msgstr ""
"Op werkdagen: Overuren worden betaald tegen 1,25 keer het normale uurloon."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:269
msgid ""
"On rest days: Overtime is compensated at 1.5 times the regular hourly wage."
msgstr ""
"Op rustdagen: Overuren worden gecompenseerd tegen 1,5 keer het normale "
"uurloon."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:271
msgid "These percentages are recorded in the input parameters model."
msgstr "Deze percentages worden vastgelegd in het invoerparametersmodel."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:274
msgid ""
"The number of overtime hours is registered as other inputs directly on "
"payslips."
msgstr ""
"Het aantal overuren wordt geregistreerd als overige invoer rechtstreeks op "
"loonstroken."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:279
msgid ""
"Provisions are the amounts computed by the employer to account for the "
"payments made to the employee for :abbr:`end-of-service (EOS)` benefits or "
"annual leaves. It is computed on a monthly basis."
msgstr ""
"Voorzieningen zijn de bedragen die de werkgever berekent om de betalingen "
"aan de werknemer voor :abbr:`einde dienst (EOS)`-uitkeringen of jaarlijks "
"verlof te verantwoorden. Dit wordt maandelijks berekend."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:282
msgid ""
"**End of service benefit provision**: This is computed by dividing the "
"monthly gross salary by 12"
msgstr ""
"**Voorziening einde dienstverband**: Deze wordt berekend door het "
"maandelijkse brutosalaris te delen door 12"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:284
msgid "\\frac{\\text{Basic} + \\text{Allowances}}{12}"
msgstr "\\frac{\\text{Basis} + \\text{Toelagen}}{12}"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:288
msgid ""
"**Annual leave provision**: This is computed by dividing the gross salary by "
"30 to get the daily salary, then multiplying that by the number of leave "
"days, and dividing the result by 12."
msgstr ""
"**Voorziening jaarlijks verlof**: Deze wordt berekend door het brutosalaris "
"te delen door 30 om het dagsalaris te krijgen, dit vervolgens te "
"vermenigvuldigen met het aantal verlofdagen en het resultaat te delen door "
"12."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:291
msgid ""
"\\left(\\frac{\\text{Basic} + \\text{Allowances}}{30}\\right)\n"
"\\times\n"
"\\left(\\frac{\\text{Number of Leave Days}}{12}\\right)"
msgstr ""
"\\left(\\frac{\\text{Basis} + \\text{Toelagen}}{30}\\right)\n"
"\\times\n"
"\\left(\\frac{\\text{Aantal verlofdagen}}{12}\\right)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:298
msgid "End of Service"
msgstr "Einde dienstverband"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:300
msgid ""
"At the end of the employee's service, if they are eligible for end-of-"
"service benefits, they should receive the following two benefits:"
msgstr ""
"Aan het einde van het dienstverband van de werknemer, als ze in aanmerking "
"komen voor einde dienstverband-uitkeringen, moeten ze de volgende twee "
"uitkeringen ontvangen:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:303
msgid ""
"**Unused leaves compensation**: The Annual Leave Balance is shown on the "
"employee's record. It is based on the annual leave type defined in the "
"**Payroll** app settings and is calculated as the total remaining "
"allocations for that specific leave type assigned to the employee."
msgstr ""
"**Compensatie voor ongebruikt verlof**: Het jaarlijkse verlofsaldo wordt "
"weergegeven op het record van de werknemer. Het is gebaseerd op het "
"jaarlijkse verloftype dat is gedefinieerd in de instellingen van de "
"**Loonadministratie**-app en wordt berekend als het totaal resterende aantal "
"toewijzingen voor dat specifieke verloftype dat aan de werknemer is "
"toegewezen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:307
msgid ""
"The balance represents the total remaining leave allocated to the employee "
"but does not reflect the portion of leave days the employee has earned up to "
"the current month."
msgstr ""
"Het saldo vertegenwoordigt het totaal resterende verlof dat aan de werknemer "
"is toegewezen, maar weerspiegelt niet het deel van de verlofdagen dat de "
"werknemer tot de huidige maand heeft opgebouwd."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:310
msgid ""
"When calculating the benefit value, the deserved leave balance is determined "
"based on the portion of the year worked. The benefit value is then "
"calculated by multiplying this deserved balance by the employee's daily rate."
msgstr ""
"Bij het berekenen van de uitkeringswaarde wordt het verdiende verlofsaldo "
"bepaald op basis van het gewerkte deel van het jaar. De uitkeringswaarde "
"wordt vervolgens berekend door dit verdiende saldo te vermenigvuldigen met "
"het dagtarief van de werknemer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:315
msgid ""
"If an employee is entitled to 14 leave days per year and has worked for 6 "
"months, they deserve 7 leave days so far. If their daily rate is 50 JOD, the "
"benefit value is: 7 days × 50 JOD = 350 JOD"
msgstr ""
"Als een werknemer recht heeft op 14 verlofdagen per jaar en 6 maanden heeft "
"gewerkt, heeft deze tot nu toe recht op 7 verlofdagen. Als het dagtarief 50 "
"JOD is, is de uitkeringswaarde: 7 dagen × 50 JOD = 350 JOD"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:320
msgid ""
"The flow mentioned above requires the allocation for the annual leave to be "
"given fully upfront in the beginning of the year for that employee"
msgstr ""
"De hierboven genoemde werkwijze vereist dat de toewijzing voor het "
"jaarlijkse verlof volledig vooraf aan het begin van het jaar aan die "
"werknemer wordt gegeven"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:323
msgid ""
"**End of Service Benefit**: The calculation begins by determining the total "
"number of days the employee has worked at the company, starting from their "
"joining date up to their last working day."
msgstr ""
"**Uitkering bij einde dienstverband**: De berekening begint met het bepalen "
"van het totale aantal dagen dat de werknemer bij het bedrijf heeft gewerkt, "
"vanaf de datum van indiensttreding tot de laatste werkdag."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:326
msgid "The total service duration is calculated out of a 365-day year."
msgstr ""
"De totale dienstduur wordt berekend op basis van een jaar van 365 dagen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:328
msgid ""
"The resulting period in years is then multiplied by the employee's gross "
"salary, which includes the basic salary and the allowances defined in the "
"payroll tab on the employee record."
msgstr ""
"De resulterende periode in jaren wordt vervolgens vermenigvuldigd met het "
"brutosalaris van de werknemer, dat het basissalaris en de toelagen omvat "
"zoals gedefinieerd op het tabblad loonadministratie in het werknemersrecord."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:331
msgid ""
"(\\text{Basic} + \\text{Allowances}) \\times \\left(\\frac{\\text{Number of "
"Days}}{365}\\right)"
msgstr ""
"(\\text{Basis} + \\text{Toelagen}) \\times \\left(\\frac{\\text{Aantal "
"dagen}}{365}\\right)"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:338
msgid ""
"Several sections within the **Payroll** app installs a Salary Structure, "
"Structure Type, Rules, and Parameters specific to Jordan."
msgstr ""
"Verschillende secties binnen de **Loonadministratie**-app installeren een "
"loonstructuur, structuurtype, regels en parameters specifiek voor Jordanië."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:342
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:328
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:220
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:144
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:315
msgid "Salary structures & structure types"
msgstr "Loonstructuren en structuurtypes"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:344
msgid ""
"When the **l10n_jo_hr_payroll** module is :ref:`installed <payroll/"
"jordan_apps>`, a new :guilabel:`Salary Structure` gets "
"installed, :guilabel:`Jordan: Monthly Pay`. This structure includes "
"one :guilabel:`Structure Type`, :guilabel:`Jordan: Employee`."
msgstr ""
"Wanneer de **l10n_jo_hr_payroll**-module :ref:`geïnstalleerd <payroll/"
"jordan_apps>` is, wordt er een nieuwe :guilabel:`loonstructuur` "
"geïnstalleerd, :guilabel:`Jordanië: Maandelijks loon`. Deze structuur bevat "
"één :guilabel:`structuurtype`, :guilabel:`Jordanië: Werknemer`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:348
msgid ""
"The :guilabel:`Salary Structure` contains all the individual :ref:`salary "
"rules <payroll/jordan_apps>` that informs the **Payroll** app how to "
"calculate employee payslips."
msgstr ""
"De :guilabel:`loonstructuur` bevat alle individuele :ref:`loonregels "
"<payroll/jordan_apps>` die de **Loonadministratie**-app informeren hoe "
"loonstroken van werknemers moeten worden berekend."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "The United States salary structure in the salary structures list."
msgstr ""
"De loonstructuur voor de Verenigde Staten in de lijst met loonstructuren."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:359
msgid ""
"To view the salary rules that inform the salary structure what to do, "
"navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Structures` "
"and expand the :guilabel:`Jordan: Employee` entry to reveal "
"the :guilabel:`Jordan: Monthly Pay` structure type. Click :guilabel:`Jordan: "
"Monthly Pay` to view the detailed salary rules."
msgstr ""
"Navigeer naar :menuselection:`Loonadministratie-app --> Configuratie --> "
"Structuren` en vouw de entry :guilabel:`Jordanië: Werknemer` uit om het "
"structuurtype :guilabel:`Jordanië: Maandelijks loon` te tonen. Klik op "
":guilabel:`Jordanië: Maandelijks loon` om de gedetailleerde loonregels te "
"bekijken."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:None
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:None
msgid "The top portion of the US salary rules."
msgstr "Het bovenste gedeelte van de Amerikaanse loonregels."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:367
msgid ""
"Each rule defines how pay is calculated, taking into account factors such as "
"allowances, deductions, and taxes."
msgstr ""
"Elke regel definieert hoe het loon wordt berekend, rekening houdend met "
"factoren zoals toelagen, inhoudingen en btw."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:373
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:252
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:177
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:407
msgid ""
"Some calculations require specific rates associated with them, or wage caps. "
"*Rules Parameters* are capable of listing a value, either a percentage or a "
"fixed amount, to reference in the salary rules."
msgstr ""
"Sommige berekeningen vereisen specifieke tarieven of loonlimieten. *Rules "
"Parameters* kunnen een waarde vermelden, hetzij een percentage hetzij een "
"vast bedrag, waarnaar in de salarisregels wordt verwezen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:377
msgid ""
"The percentage rate for employee Social Security deductions is set in the "
"`Jordan Social Security Employee Deduction Rate %` parameter."
msgstr ""
"Het percentage voor werknemersaftrek van de sociale zekerheid is ingesteld "
"in de parameter `Jordanië sociale zekerheid werknemersaftrekpercentage %`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:380
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:365
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:255
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:414
msgid ""
"Most rules pull information stored in the parameters module to get the rate "
"of the rule (a percentage) and the cap (a dollar amount)."
msgstr ""
"De meeste regels halen informatie op die is opgeslagen in de parametermodule "
"om het tarief van de regel (een percentage) en de limiet (een dollarbedrag) "
"te verkrijgen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:383
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:368
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:258
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:183
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:417
msgid ""
"To view rule parameters, navigate to :menuselection:`Payroll app --> "
"Configuration --> Rule Parameters`. Here, all rule parameters are displayed "
"with their linked :guilabel:`Salary Rules`, which can be accessed. Review "
"the parameters associated with a rule by looking for the :guilabel:`Name` of "
"the rule, and make any edits as needed."
msgstr ""
"Ga naar :menuselection:`Payroll app --> Configuration --> Rule Parameters` "
"om regelparameters te bekijken. Hier worden alle regelparameters weergegeven "
"met hun gekoppelde :guilabel:`Salary Rules`, die toegankelijk zijn. Bekijk "
"de parameters die aan een regel zijn gekoppeld door te zoeken naar de "
":guilabel:`Name` van de regel en breng indien nodig wijzigingen aan."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:389
msgid ""
"Odoo adds updated rule parameters for the current calendar year. It is "
"**not** recommended to edit rule parameters **unless a national parameter "
"has changed**, and is different from the rule parameters created by Odoo. "
"Check with all national regulations *before* making any changes to rule "
"parameters."
msgstr ""
"Odoo voegt bijgewerkte regelparameters toe voor het huidige kalenderjaar. "
"Het wordt **niet** aanbevolen om regelparameters te bewerken **tenzij een "
"nationale parameter is gewijzigd** en verschilt van de regelparameters die "
"door Odoo zijn aangemaakt. Controleer alle nationale regelgeving *voordat* "
"je wijzigingen aanbrengt in regelparameters."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:395
msgid "Run Jordan payroll"
msgstr "Voer de Jordaanse loonadministratie uit"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:397
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:409
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:285
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:339
msgid ""
"Before running payroll, the payroll officer must validate "
"employee :doc:`work entries <../work_entries>` to confirm pay accuracy and "
"catch errors. This includes checking that all time off is approved and any "
"overtime is appropriate."
msgstr ""
"Voordat je de loonadministratie uitvoert, moet de "
"loonadministratieverantwoordelijke :doc:`werkvermeldingen <../work_entries>` "
"van werknemers valideren om de nauwkeurigheid van de betaling te bevestigen "
"en fouten op te sporen. Dit omvat het controleren of al het verlof is "
"goedgekeurd en of eventuele overuren passend zijn."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:401
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:413
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:289
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:343
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:441
msgid ""
"Work entries sync based on the employee's :doc:`contract <../contracts>` "
"configuration. Odoo pulls from the assigned working schedule, attendance "
"records, planning schedule, and approved time off."
msgstr ""
"Werkvermeldingen synchroniseren op basis van de :doc:`contract <../contracts>"
"`configuratie van de werknemer. Odoo haalt gegevens op uit het toegewezen "
"werkrooster, aanwezigheidsregistraties, planningsschema en goedgekeurd "
"verlof."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:404
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:416
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:444
msgid ""
"Any :ref:`discrepencies or conflicts <payroll/conflicts>` must be resolved, "
"then the work entries can be :ref:`regenerated <payroll/regenerate-work-"
"entries>`."
msgstr ""
"Eventuele :ref:`discrepanties of conflicten <payroll/conflicts>` moeten "
"worden opgelost, waarna de werkvermeldingen opnieuw kunnen worden "
":ref:`gegenereerd <payroll/regenerate-work-entries>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:407
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:419
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:295
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/turkey.rst:349
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:447
msgid ""
"Once everything is correct, draft payslips can be :ref:`created individually "
"<payroll/process>` or in :doc:`groups <../pay_runs>`, referred to in the "
"**Payroll** app as *Pay Runs*."
msgstr ""
"Zodra alles correct is, kunnen conceptloonstroken :ref:`individueel <payroll/"
"process>` of in :doc:`groepen <../pay_runs>` worden aangemaakt, waarnaar in "
"de **Loonadministratie** app wordt verwezen als *Betaalrondes*."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:440
msgid ""
"The accounting process when running payroll has two "
"components: :ref:`creating journal entries <payroll/jo-journal>`, "
"and :ref:`registering payments <payroll/jo-register>`."
msgstr ""
"Het boekhoudproces bij het uitvoeren van de loonadministratie heeft twee "
"onderdelen: :ref:`boekingen aanmaken <payroll/jo-journal>`, en "
":ref:`betalingen registreren <payroll/jo-register>`."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:458
msgid ""
"Thirteen accounts from the Jordan :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` are "
"included with the Jordan payroll localization:"
msgstr ""
"Dertien rekeningen uit het Jordaanse :abbr:`grootboekschema (Chart of "
"Accounts)` zijn opgenomen in de Jordaanse loonadministratielokalisatie:"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:461
msgid "`500301 Basic Salary`: Tracks the basic wages paid to employees."
msgstr ""
"`500301 Basissalaris`: Houdt de basislonen bij die aan werknemers worden "
"betaald."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:462
msgid ""
"`500302 Housing Allowance`: Captures housing allowance payments provided to "
"employees."
msgstr ""
"`500302 Huisvestingstoeslag`: Legt betalingen van huisvestingstoelagen vast "
"die aan werknemers worden verstrekt."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:463
msgid ""
"`500303 Transportation Allowance`: Captures transportation allowance "
"payments to employees."
msgstr ""
"`500303 Vervoerstoeslag`: Legt betalingen van vervoerstoelagen aan "
"werknemers vast."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:464
msgid ""
"`500308 Staff Other Allowances`: Covers employee allowances that do not fit "
"any other available categories."
msgstr ""
"`500308 Overige toelagen voor personeel`: Dekt werknemerstoelagen die niet "
"in een andere beschikbare categorie passen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:466
msgid ""
"`500310 Salary Deductions`: Reflects deductions applied to employee salaries "
"(e.g., advances, fines, statutory deductions)."
msgstr ""
"`500310 Salarisinhoudingen`: Weerspiegelt inhoudingen die worden toegepast "
"op salarissen van werknemers (bv. voorschotten, boetes, wettelijke "
"inhoudingen)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:468
msgid ""
"`500305 Leave Salary`: Records salaries actually paid to employees while on "
"paid leave."
msgstr ""
"`500305 Verlofssalaris`: Registreert salarissen die daadwerkelijk aan "
"werknemers worden uitbetaald tijdens betaald verlof."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:469
msgid ""
"`201022 Social Security Payable`: Holds both employee and employer amounts "
"payable for social insurance contributions."
msgstr ""
"`201022 Te betalen sociale zekerheid`: Bevat zowel de werknemers- als "
"werkgeversbedragen die verschuldigd zijn voor sociale verzekeringsbijdragen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:471
msgid ""
"`200502 Leave Days Provision`: Accrues the cost of paid leave; the balance "
"is reduced when leave is taken, and any leave not taken may be paid out when "
"the employee leaves the company."
msgstr ""
"`200502 Verlofsdagenvoorziening`: Bouwt de kosten van betaald verlof op; het "
"saldo wordt verlaagd wanneer verlof wordt opgenomen, en eventueel niet "
"opgenomen verlof kan worden uitbetaald wanneer de werknemer het bedrijf "
"verlaat."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:473
msgid ""
"`200503 End of Service Provision`: Accumulates the end-of-service benefit "
"monthly, so the amount can be paid (partially or fully) when the employee "
"leaves, per service length and reason."
msgstr ""
"`200503 Einde-dienstverbandvoorziening`: Bouwt de einde-"
"dienstverbanduitkering maandelijks op, zodat het bedrag (gedeeltelijk of "
"volledig) kan worden uitbetaald wanneer de werknemer vertrekt, afhankelijk "
"van de duur van het dienstverband en de reden."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:475
msgid ""
"`200101 Payables`: Shows amounts payable to employees as salaries (unpaid "
"salary liability at period end)."
msgstr ""
"`200101 Crediteuren`: Toont bedragen die verschuldigd zijn aan werknemers "
"als salarissen (onbetaalde salarisverplichtingen aan het einde van de "
"periode)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:477
msgid ""
"`500202 End of Service Indemnity`: Captures company expenses set aside to "
"fund end-of-service benefits (expense-side counterpart to the provision)."
msgstr ""
"`500202 Einde-dienstverband schadevergoeding`: Legt de kosten vast die het "
"bedrijf opzij zet om einde-dienstverbanduitkeringen te financieren (de "
"kostenkant van de voorziening)."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:479
msgid ""
"`200307 Employee Income Tax`: Accumulates the income tax amount withheld "
"from the employee's salary."
msgstr ""
"`200307 Inkomstenbelasting werknemers`: Bouwt het bedrag aan "
"inkomstenbelasting op dat is ingehouden op het salaris van de werknemer."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:481
msgid ""
"`500311 Social Security Expenses`: Captures The total expense amount from "
"payments to the social insurance authority."
msgstr ""
"`500311 Sociale zekerheidskosten`: Legt het totale kostenbedrag vast van "
"betalingen aan de sociale verzekeringsinstantie."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:484
msgid ""
"The :abbr:`CoA (Chart of Accounts)` configuration is done by default when "
"installing the Jordan payroll localization. The account codes and names can "
"be edited to suit the company's needs."
msgstr ""
"De :abbr:`CoA (Grootboekschema)`-configuratie is standaard gedaan bij het "
"installeren van de Jordaanse loonadministratielokalisatie. Rekeningcodes en "
"namen kunnen worden aangepast aan de behoeften van het bedrijf."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:488
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/mexico.rst:504
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/saudi_arabia.rst:375
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:516
msgid ""
"If everything seems correct on the journal entry draft, post the journal "
"entries."
msgstr "Als alles correct lijkt in het boekingsconcept, boek dan de boekingen."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:498
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:526
msgid ""
"After the :ref:`journal entries <payroll/journal>` are validated, Odoo can "
"generate payments."
msgstr ""
"Nadat de :ref:`boekingen <payroll/journal>` zijn gevalideerd, kan Odoo "
"betalingen genereren."

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:511
#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/united_states.rst:544
msgid "Reports"
msgstr "Rapportages"

#: ../../content/applications/hr/payroll/payroll_localizations/jordan.rst:513
msgid ""
"No additional payroll reports unique to the Jordan payroll localization "
"exist. All reports are the standard preconfigured reports included with the "
"**Payroll** app."
msgstr ""
"Er bestaan geen aanvullende loonadministratierapporten die uniek zijn voor "
"de Jordaanse loonadministratielokalisatie. Alle rapporten zijn de standaard "
"vooraf geconfigureerde rapporten die zijn inbegrepen bij de "
"**Loonadministratie**-app."

